# Deny by default -- only explicitly allowed files are committed
*

# Committed project files
!.gitignore
!config.json
# work-item-format.md and schedule-format.md are intentionally NOT allowlisted
# in this dogfood repo: canonical sources live at core/docs/*.md, and the
# copies under .ninthwave/ are scaffold-generated mirrors that `nw init`
# writes. Consumer repos DO allowlist them (see the template in
# core/commands/init.ts), because they don't have the canonical sources.
!work/
!work/**
!schedules/
!schedules/**
!friction/
!friction/**
